description:
Movie: After Earth 2013
This has been trimmed down to 30 minutes. All the extra crap that M. Night thought he needed to have in the movie was removed. Only the parts essential the the story and most action sequences have been left in. One scene (Cypher Rage checking his leg) was reordered for story correctness. 
I like this version of the movie better than the long drawn out boring version that M. Night decieded to release. 
Two people that should STOP be allowed to make movies: M. Night and JJ Abrams. Actually JJ Abrams is pretty good if he could put down the fucking flashlight. Lost was great.
 
Anyway. on with the show!
